ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada - Republic of Rwanda on Air Transport ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF THE REPUBLIC OF RWANDA ON AIR TRANSPORT; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Agreement.
AttachmentsAttachment
